### Phase 2：页面入口 - 根路径应返回聊天页 HTML
GET http://localhost:8044/
Accept: text/html

### Phase 2：页面入口 - /chat 应返回聊天页 HTML
GET http://localhost:8044/chat
Accept: text/html

### Phase 2：静态资源 - 前端脚本应可访问
GET http://localhost:8044/js/chat.js
Accept: application/javascript

### Fallback：同步接口 - 一轮直接生成 itinerary
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "message": "杭州3天，预算3000，轻松一点，想吃美食和看自然风景"
}

### Fallback：同步接口 - 首轮只给目的地，响应中应包含 followUpQuestion 和 missingFields
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "message": "我想去杭州"
}

### Phase 2：流式接口 - 首轮触发追问，观察 answer 事件中是否直接包含具体追问文案，并记录返回的 sessionId
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "北京5天，预算3000"
}

### Phase 2：流式接口 - 预算追问后只回复数字，应该识别为 budget，不应继续追问预算
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "sessionId": "请替换为上一步返回的 sessionId",
  "message": "300"
}

### Phase 2：流式接口 - 如果仍缺偏好，再补一个偏好后应生成 itinerary
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "sessionId": "请替换为同一个 sessionId",
  "message": "轻松一点，喜欢美食"
}

### Phase 2：流式接口 - 使用同一 sessionId 修改 itinerary，观察 status / itinerary / done
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "sessionId": "请替换为同一个 sessionId",
  "message": "第二天太累了，轻松一点"
}

### Phase 2：流式接口 - 旅行天数追问后只回复数字，应该识别为 tripDays
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "我想去上海，预算3000"
}

### Phase 2：流式接口 - 使用上一步返回的 sessionId，仅回复数字天数
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "sessionId": "请替换为上一步返回的 sessionId",
  "message": "3"
}

### 边界：空消息应返回 400
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "message": ""
}

### 边界：同步接口缺失 message 应返回 400
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "phase1-boundary-missing-message"
}

### 边界：同步接口空请求体应返回 400
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


### 边界：流式接口空消息也应返回 error 事件或 400
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": ""
}

### 边界：流式接口缺失 message 应返回 error 事件或 400
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "sessionId": "phase2-boundary-missing-message"
}

### 边界：不传 sessionId，应自动创建新会话
POST http://localhost:8044/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "message": "上海周末两天，想拍照打卡"
}
